					<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/AdobeStock_90138561-300x300.jpeg" alt=""/>
				</a>
			</div>
						<a class="post_more_title" href="https://lithub.com/notable-literary-deaths-in-2024/">
				<h7 style="display:block;">Notable Literary Deaths in 2024</h7>
			</a>
			To the members of the literary community we lost this year, we say a last thank you, and goodbye. You will be missed.
*
Poet,...			
			</div>
